@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((v2 + 1.00 / v0 + 0.07) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.34)) + ((v0 + 0.81 / v2 + 0.71) - (v2 + 0.84 * v1 + 0.64)))
    tmp = wp.abs((v0 * v1))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.cos(0.65))
    v2 = 0.43
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.18 + tmp + 0.06) - (v0 + 0.26 * v1 + 0.70)) / ((v0 + 0.96 - v2 + 0.58) + 0.51))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.55)))
    data[tid] = v0
